      "seed": 1591731168,
      "version": 73,
      "versionNonce": 294999584,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770601046352,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The Invalidators\n\nNatural Expiry: The max-age reaches zero.\nFingerprinting: You change the filename (e.g., style.v2.css). This is a new life cycle because it's a \n                \"different\" file to the cache.\nManual Purge: You tell Cloudflare, \"Delete everything you know about index.html.\" \n              This forces Cloudflare to go back to your Origin Pods for a fresh copy.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The Invalidators\n\nNatural Expiry: The max-age reaches zero.\nFingerprinting: You change the filename (e.g., style.v2.css). This is a new life cycle because it's a \n                \"different\" file to the cache.\nManual Purge: You tell Cloudflare, \"Delete everything you know about index.html.\" \n              This forces Cloudflare to go back to your Origin Pods for a fresh copy.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
